<br>
If you like what you hear and think you have the same attitutes as we do, read our <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.ebonmoon.com/registration.htm">admission guidelines.</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
Read our <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub95.ezboard.com/febonmoonfrm12.showMessage?topicID=21.topic">Frequently Asked Quesions</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
If you think we may be suitable for you, get started right away by creating your character profile at <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.guildmagic.com">Guild Magic</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
Be certain to associate our guild in your preferences. Then the profile will be sent to us.<br>
<br>
---------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
Now you have done all the above and are wondering how to make contact with us. The initial thing we will do is evaluate your Guildmagic information. It needs to be done FIRST (Read the <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub95.ezboard.com/febonmoonfrm12.showMessage?topicID=19.topic">Guildmagic FAQ</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->. <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Mail your character screenshot to <!--EZCODE MAIL START--><a href="mailto: chimerapop@aol.com"> chimerapop@aol.com</a><!--EZCODE MAIL END-->.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
Next, contact us here on this message board in the  <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub95.ezboard.com/febonmoonfrm20">Foyer</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->. This tells us you have registered for EZ Board.<br>
<br>
To get invited, show up at one of our guild meetings in North Karana. We have council near the wooden bridge, just off the trail ((Every Wednesday @ 7pm Pacific)). Please try to let us know you are coming in advance, if possible. Make sure you have done all of the above first. If the guildmagic profile isn't completed do not bother to show up, you will not be admitted.<br>
<br>
After we invite you at the meeting, you will be on a probation for a period of two weeks. When this time is past, our members will vote and you will need 6 votes to become permanent. It is in your best interest to be as active as possible during this period.<br>
<br>
If you have any questions or inquiries concerning our policies, feel free to send me a tell. You can also have a bard deliver a scroll to <!--EZCODE MAIL START--><a href="mailto: Chimerapop@aol.com"> Chimerapop@aol.com</a><!--EZCODE MAIL END--> <br>
